#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yve.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.yve"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:1 of
msgid "Exponentially scaled Bessel function of the second kind of real order."
msgstr "实数阶第二类指数缩放的贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns the exponentially scaled Bessel function of the second kind of "
"real order `v` at complex `z`::"
msgstr "返回在复数 `z` 处实数阶 `v` 的第二类指数缩放贝塞尔函数值::"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yve.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:8 of
msgid "Order (float)."
msgstr "阶数（浮点数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:10 of
msgid "Argument (float or complex)."
msgstr "自变量（浮点数或复数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:12 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function results"
msgstr "用于函数结果的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yve.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:15 of
msgid "**Y** -- Value of the exponentially scaled Bessel function."
msgstr "**Y** -- 指数缩放的贝塞尔函数值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.yve.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`yv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:21 of
msgid "Unscaled Bessel function of the second kind of real order."
msgstr "实数阶第二类未缩放的贝塞尔函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:25 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For positive `v` values, the computation is carried out using the AMOS "
"[1]_ `zbesy` routine, which exploits the connection to the Hankel Bessel "
"functions :math:`H_v^{(1)}` and :math:`H_v^{(2)}`,"
msgstr ""
"对于正 `v` 值，计算使用 AMOS [1]_ 的 `zbesy` 例程，该例程利用了与汉克尔"
"贝塞尔函数 :math:`H_v^{(1)}` 和 :math:`H_v^{(2)}` 的关系，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:29 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Y_v(z) = \\frac{1}{2\\imath} (H_v^{(1)} - H_v^{(2)}).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:31 of
msgid "For negative `v` values the formula,"
msgstr "对于负 `v` 值，使用公式，"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:33 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Y_{-v}(z) = Y_v(z) \\cos(\\pi v) + J_v(z) \\sin(\\pi v)\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:35 of
msgid ""
"is used, where :math:`J_v(z)` is the Bessel function of the first kind, "
"computed using the AMOS routine `zbesj`.  Note that the second term is "
"exactly zero for integer `v`; to improve accuracy the second term is "
"explicitly omitted for `v` values such that `v = floor(v)`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`J_v(z)` 是第一类贝塞尔函数，使用 AMOS 例程 `zbesj` 计算。注意"
"，对于整数 `v`，第二项恰好为零；为了提高精度，当 `v = floor(v)` 时，显式"
"省略第二项。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:40 of
msgid ""
"Exponentially scaled Bessel functions are useful for large `z`: for "
"these, the unscaled Bessel functions can easily under-or overflow."
msgstr ""
"指数缩放的贝塞尔函数在 `z` 较大时很有用：对于这些情况，未缩放的贝塞尔函数"
"很容易下溢或上溢。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:44 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.bessel.yve:45 of
msgid ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, A Portable Package for Bessel Functions of a "
"Complex Argument and Nonnegative Order\", http://netlib.org/amos/"
msgstr ""
"Donald E. Amos, \"AMOS, 一个用于复数自变量和非负阶贝塞尔函数的可移植包\","
" http://netlib.org/amos/"

